title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Add a table to the report.
2. In the group row of the table, add a highlight rule and a map rule.
3. Preview the attached report.
4. Attempt to export the data from the table and observe the exception being thrown.
